Playing Zork

From the Zork portal, type:

  enter portal

Once inside, commands are interpreted by the Zork parser.  Common commands
include:

  look
  inventory
  take <object>
  drop <object>
  open <object>
  close <object>
  read <object>
  score
  north, south, east, west, up, down

Session commands:

  zork save
  zork restore
  zork reset
  zork exit
  zork help [topic]

Zork inventory is separate from normal Darkwind inventory.
